  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0ba8\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bc6\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bae\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bc7\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0b92\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0bb0\u0bae\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0ba9\u0bc6\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b85\u0baa\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb8\u0bcd\u0bb8 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0ba3",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Risk of Ranil Wickramasinghe pushing ahead with the agreements he could not make with the US in good governance - Thissa Vidarana",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Ranil Wickramasinghe is in danger of making agreements with the United States that could not be concluded in a good governance government. Tissa Vidarana, President of the Lanka Sama Samaj Party and Member of Parliament, said that people should be ready to stop any deals that are dangerous to the country.",
        "He said this while attending a press conference held by the Socialist People's Front in Colombo yesterday (26).",
        "Ranil Wickremesinghe was elected President with a majority of Parliament without a popular mandate. When the United National Party did not have any member of the Parliament, Rajapakse through the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna helped to appoint him to the post of President.",
        "Podujana Party Vice President Basil Rajapaksh is a US citizen. He himself has worked from behind to bring his party into harmony to make Ranil Wickramasinghe the President. Ranil Wickramasinghe is currently working to carry the government in the manner required by America.",
        "Also, Ranil Wickramasinghe had planned to make 3 agreements with the United States in the government of good governance. The Akta contract was signed, while the other two contracts, MCC and SOBA, were abandoned due to popular opposition.",
        "Both these deals are a huge risk to the country. There is a danger that our lands will be sold to America through the MCC agreement. Similarly, through the SOFA agreement, the US Army is allowed to enter our country without any hindrance.",
        "Also, Ranil Wickramasinghe, who was prime minister in the good governance government, is currently the president of the country. So there is a fear that he will repeat these deals which are dangerous for the country.",
        "If Ranil Wickramasinghe tries to make such deals which are dangerous for the country, people should prepare to stop it.",
        "And the government should take quick steps to solve the problems of the people in the economic crisis that the country is facing. We are ready to support the good programs of the government to solve the problems of the people.",
        "On the contrary, if the country is sold to America, we will fight with the people against it."
      ],
